        {
          "title": "Scott Pilgrim vs. the World",
          "year": 2010,
          "by": "Sean Fennessey",
          "note": "Edgar Wright as if John Hughes designed a Nintendo game; a box-office bomb loaded with future stars (Winstead, Culkin, Evans, Larson, Plaza). Worth remembering it exists."
